- 'Main.sublime-menu' has a 'Key Bindings' entry for 'Default (File Browser).sublime-keymap' without 'args.user_file' set. For non-standard keymap names this is required because edit_settings will otherwise create that filename in User, but Sublime Text will not load it. Set 'args.user_file' to '${packages}/User/Default (${platform}).sublime-keymap'.
